title: Rebio - Holandska
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Western, Buffet, Salad bar, Juice bar
description: One of several Rebio self-serve restaurants, all of which are vegetarian. This one is located in the modern Spielberk office park. Air-conditioned, has Wi-Fi, uses mostly organic produce. The venue has 86 seats, atmosphere is a bit like a modern canteen. Limited vegan options.
